  09 Oct 2014; Michael Weber <xmw@gentoo.org> +files/spek-0.8.3-stdlib.patch,
  spek-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Include stdlib.h for malloc and free (bug 519450)

  20 Aug 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> spek-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Escape newline.

  03 Aug 2013; Michael Weber <xmw@gentoo.org> spek-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Require gcc:4.7 or newer (bug 479500).

  03 Aug 2013; Michael Weber <xmw@gentoo.org>
  +files/spek-0.8.3-replace-gnu+11-with-c++11.patch, spek-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Replace -std=gnu+11 with -srd=c++11 for bug 479500.

*spek-0.8.3 (28 Jul 2013)

